@node "AMAZING SPIDERMAN"
AMAZING SPIDERMAN

On the high score table type "generic".  (I'm not sure if this means type it
or enter it as your name, so try `em both.)  Now when you press 'Help' during
play you'll receive full energy.
@endnode
